    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Providing a border or case to surround, support, enclose, or call attention to such items as a work of art, mirror, or document, leaving the item itself visible.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
